That doesn't explain much but before this code we call `Tuple<DocumentParserContext, XContentBuilder> tuple = XContentDataHelper.cloneSubContext(context);` which goes here https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/c7f2225c3c398ab7c6d26f80e999503307b6a951/server/src/main/java/org/elasticsearch/index/mapper/XContentDataHelper.java#L138 and _this_ call produces malformed document that can be seen in the exception: `[{"ulong"},{"ulong":1}]`. Notice how first `ulong` has no value.

