```
although according to the documentation it is integer (32 bit).  
> took
(integer) How long, in milliseconds, it took to process the bulk request.

https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/docs-bulk.html

This causes the Jackson parse exception in our internal library (the official Elastic `ElasticsearchClient` uses `long` internally).
Even if I fix it to be `long` in our library the value seems to be odd: something completed within `6,641,016,797` ms? 

